%3Fstory_fbid%3D2640629789347426%26id%3D124616407615456&d=%2BaoNGjxKkOyNIKnkVXg3cTQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=8cbe5d2e\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2640629789347426&amp;id=124616407615456</a><br />\n<br />\nPost：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eDEkrT\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eDEkrT</a><br />\n<br />\n//平等機會婦女聯席發言人區美寶稱，3個組織11月初共同發起控訴警察性暴力的國際聯署，截至本月7日收集到21國共85個團體聯署支持。為了向聯合國專家展開更有力游說，3個組織呼籲受害者主動聯絡他們並接受訪談，強調會保密。//<br />\n<br />\n我們現正收集抗爭者在抗爭期間／被捕後遭受警察性暴力對待的資料，作以下用途：<br />\n1. 協助受害人可以完整保留該事件之紀錄<br />\n2. 整理資料並製成 #ProtestToo 實錄，以作追究之用<br />\n3. 收集國際聯署（進行中），結合個案提交聯合國，爭取國際間關注及支持<br />\n4. 要求香港政府獨立、公正地徹查「反送中運動」發生的性暴力<br />\n<br />\n*個人資料及通訊紀錄在實錄完成後可按受訪者意願全部銷毀<br />\n詳情及相關安排請聯絡Tg @protesttoo"},{"pid":"4ab95be436623ce5d4a354a5b49f6838bb41ccba","tid":1777871,"uid":171742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T15:17:16.000Z","msg":"無限悲傷，英年早逝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4697223ee1f6fa03cb68f4070deae6112f4df705","tid":1777871,"uid":171742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T15:17:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"488155c9235fd3528668a656b279e7e7065e4a13","tid":1777871,"uid":302471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T15:19:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24165f3c4b3d8f676d8338ba9ca7d39a8702db60","tid":1777871,"uid":34517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3038a40668a974645c9ae1566504bda64594f49","tid":1777871,"uid":60924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"130c5746cb5c0c3d9f3b27fd5b2ec07c6ea068d3","tid":1777871,"uid":34517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T14:19:48.000Z","msg":"想問下大圍邊度坐巴士？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T14:58:47.000Z","msg":"大圍港鐵站 D、F 或 G 出口的免費接駁巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass